{"tid":1690446,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"光敏感性癲癇","createTime":"2019-11-03T10:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:40:21.000Z","uid":49196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c025c73b72f1ac07b824e2354cb492520622cec9","tid":1690446,"uid":49196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"閃爍的光源<br />\n<br />\n電視、電影、電玩等往往為了娛樂效果，會在內容中設計複雜的聲光效果，然而，頻繁閃爍的光線可能會影響腦部的正常放電機制。<br />\n<br />\n這種由光線導致的癲癇稱作「光敏性癲癇 (photosensitive epilepsy)」。歷史上有個著名的案例名為「3D龍事件」，1997年12月16日傍晚，數百名日本兒童在觀賞動畫《神奇寶貝（現譯為精靈寶可夢）》的戰鬥片段後，陸續出現癲癇症狀而緊急送醫。由於該片段充斥頻繁閃光，特效過強的特定集數因而被禁播。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實有冇得用呢個做理由申請禁制令，禁止d狗用電筒係咁閃？"},{"pid":"576a9df1d23255695d19fa47f538d68847103dca","tid":1690446,"uid":73100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"如果肯日頭打仗就起碼唔洗驚佢支電筒"},{"pid":"243045e894823f0790aa2c7f80ae5fdd5e3ec0e1","tid":1690446,"uid":49196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"已經蒙面蒙到咁，冇得用驚俾人起底做藉口啦？"},{"pid":"9de9bd25ea07a8829c2637ddde4768c52fe67240","tid":1690446,"uid":49196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"576a9df1d23255695d19fa47f538d68847103dca","tid":1690446,"uid":73100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"如果肯日頭打仗就起碼唔洗驚佢支電筒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"日頭都照開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d399d192be63425464788c84e930134e518e677","tid":1690446,"uid":73100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de9bd25ea07a8829c2637ddde4768c52fe67240","tid":1690446,"uid":49196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"576a9df1d23255695d19fa47f538d68847103dca","tid":1690446,"uid":73100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"如果肯日頭打仗就起碼唔洗驚佢支電筒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"日頭都照開啦<img 